Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.Activity
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.Course
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Conflict, java.lang.Comparable<Course>
    public class Course
extends Activity
implements java.lang.Comparable<Course>
    A Course class extend Activity and contains a course's information including name, section, credits, meeting days and times, and instructorID. The class has functionality to get and set all fields (some are set by calling super), as well as display information about a Course and check for duplicates.
    Since:
    2021-08-24
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
